    <studytitle>The difference between resistance and aerobic training on physical and perceived outcomes in adolescents with chronic fatigue syndrome. A pilot study.</studytitle>
    <scientifictitle>The difference between resistance and aerobic training on physical and perceived outcomes in adolescents with chronic fatigue syndrome. A pilot study.</scientifictitle>
